author: wn.com
title: Bill Clinton to stump for Hillary on campaign trail in Iowa
text: Former President Bill Clinton will join Hillary Rodham Clinton on the campaign trail in Iowa this weekend, making his first visit to the state in support of his wife's 2016 Democratic run for president. Mrs. Clinton's campaign announced Monday that Mr. Clinton would deliver remarks at a campaign rally ahead ... ...
